yingyinNormal.zh: 杰说你一心想进我们公司。

yingyinNormal.en: So you're determined to dig in your heels. I am sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你是打算固执己见了，很抱歉。

yingyinNormal.en: He's sure determined to get to his meeting. He's about to do something rash.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他看来是非参会不可，要不顾一切了。

yingyinNormal.en: So many estates are going under these days and I'm just determined that Downton won't be one of them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如今很多庄园都没落了，我决心不让唐顿也如此。

yingyinNormal.en: Since you're determined to meet her, you're about to find out. Eyes on Eurus Holmes. Governor's orders.
yingyinNormal.zh: 既然你铁了心要见她，你很快就能知道了。检查欧罗斯·福尔摩斯。主管有令。

yingyinNormal.en: And it's unbelievable to think that our happiness is not determined by what we have, but what we don't have.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很难想象我们的满足感不是来自我们拥有的东西，而是没有得到的。

yingyinNormal.en: That's the American dream. That's what this country was built on. And that's what we're determined to restore.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是美国梦。这也是这个国家的立国之本。也是我们矢志追求的重建经济社会的目标。

yingyinNormal.en: I felt strong, in control. I told Bryce what I thought and I was determined not to talk to him for the rest of the evening.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得自己能掌控一切 我告诉布莱斯我的想法，也决心晚上不再跟他说话。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't pretend to take the credit, Mr Drewe. It was His Lordship who was determined you should stay. You owe your thanks to him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可不敢居功，德鲁先生，坚持让你留下的是老爷，你应该感谢他。

yingyinNormal.en: Certainly. I've run from bullies, dogs, angry chickens, and one particularly persistent P.E. teacher determined to bend me over and give me a scoliosis test.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然跑过，我被恶霸，狗和暴走的鸡追过，还有个锲而不舍执意要给我做脊柱侧弯测试的体育老师。

yingyinNormal.en: If it is determined that chemical or biological weapons have been used in the Syrian conflict, then from this moment forward, the United States will be morally obligated to intervene.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果得到确认叙利亚冲突中用到了生化武器，那么从此刻起，美国将有道德义务插手。

yingyinNormal.en: I have to admit, I was a little miffed that Claire grabbed the good seat, especially after I gave her such a magical weekend, but I was determined to stay positive. And then it hit me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不得不承认，我有点生气克莱尔居然选择了好座位，特别是我刚给她制造了一个魔幻般的周末，但我决心要保持乐观之后，我突然想到[打中了我]。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, you're all valued employees. But as we undergo this transition to LIFE online we wanted to be candid with you that some of you will be determined non-vital employees to the new partnership.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，你们都是很有能力的员工。但是，当我们在将周刊网路化的过渡期间，我们要向你们坦白的说。

yingyinNormal.en: If you, dear father, do not take the trouble to check her, she'll be fixed forever as the silliest and most determined flirt who ever made her family ridiculous. And Kitty will follow, as she always does.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果爸爸你不制止她，她会被挂上愚蠢的卖俏者的花名，弄得我们全家都惹人笑话的。吉蒂也会一如既往地跟随着。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: The food police are <highlight>determined</highlight> that this enjoyment should be rendered yet another quality pleasure guaranteed to damage our health.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 食品监管局确信这种乐趣又是另一种必定会损害我们健康的“罪恶的”快乐。

examination_example.sentence: He had to suffer many disappointments and rejections along the way, but these made him all the more <highlight>determined</highlight> to succeed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一路上他不得不遭受许多失望和拒绝，但这些使他更加坚定了成功的决心。

examination_example.sentence: Students also benefit from learning something about coding before they get to college, which can drive the less-experienced or -<highlight>determined</highlight> students away.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 学生们还受益于在他们上大学之前学习一些关于编码的知识，这可能会把经验不足或意志不坚定的学生赶走。
